title: Judy Blue Women's High Waist Front Yoke Retro Wide Leg Jeans
description: The Judy Blue Women's High Waist Front Yoke Retro Wide Leg Jeans are a must-have addition to your wardrobe for enduring comfort and timeless style. Crafted with a super stretchy fabric, and featuring a retro wide leg silouhette with unique yoke pattern on the front, these jeans effortlessly combine comfort with fashion-forward flair. Available in a medium blue wash, they're designed to make a statement wherever you go.
